            <abstract>
                <p>Qǝne of the mawaddǝs-type, which is preserved in full and with type indication in the edition of 
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Afawarq1984Yageezqeneyat"/><citedRange unit="page">307</citedRange></bibl> and with no more
                    than its last two verses in <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFabb145"/>, f. 55rb. Having 9 verses, this qǝne is defined as a mawaddǝs 
                    kʷǝllǝkǝmu-type according to the classification of <bibl><ptr target="bm:Guidi1900Qene"/>
                     <citedRange unit="page">4-5</citedRange></bibl>. The author is not indicated.</p>
